translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ７日目の夜
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Night of the 7th day

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全然到着しないのでしびれをきらしたランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance, irritated by their complete failure to arrive,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東芝王子の報告ミスで日と月が間違っていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Found out Prince Toshiba’s report mistakenly switched the day and month.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹が魔王になってしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Miki has become the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: みんなを逃がすランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance lets everyone escape.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは魔王美樹と対峙する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance confronts Demon King Miki.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 結局全員で美樹を戦う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the end, everyone fights Miki together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＪＡＰＡＮ城、ランス達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: JAPAN Castle, Lance and the others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 橋のおかげで守れているが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are being protected thanks to the bridge,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 橋のおかげで攻め込む事も出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But because of the bridge, they cannot attack either.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達の拠点ＪＡＰＡＮ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance's base, JAPAN.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、魔物の猛攻と妖怪の内乱でついて滅亡
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, it was destroyed due to a fierce monster assault and a yokai internal conflict.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物界、ケイブリスの本拠地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Monster World, Cavebris's stronghold.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスの美樹への暴力と陵辱が続く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cavebris continues to abuse and violate Miki.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物界、ケイブリスの本拠地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Monster World, Cavebris's stronghold.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹を殺してついにケイブリスが魔王になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Having killed Miki, Cavebris finally became the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、参謀本部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, General Staff Headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各地の軍の再配置を進めている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rearranging troops from various areas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ４地域から魔軍を全て追い出した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They have driven out all the demon armies from the four regions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、問題は解決した訳では無い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, the problem has not been solved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, Command Center.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスが魔物界に攻め込む作戦を発表する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance announces a plan to invade the Monster World.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, Command Center.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各地から兵力２０万を集める
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gathering 200,000 troops from various regions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦争の準備を進めています
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are preparing for war.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 番裏の砦、ヘルマン＆リーザス軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ban'ura Fort, Hermann & Liezas army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジノライン、ゼス＆自由都市＆ＪＡＰＡＮ軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maginot Line, Zess, Free City, and JAPAN armies.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの指示で突撃開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Charge begins under Lance's orders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 序盤の戦況状況
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Situation in the early stages of the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類は勢いで攻め込み、志気も高い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Human forces are attacking with momentum and high morale.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍は数は居るが志気は低い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon army has numbers but low morale.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、魔物界のどこか・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, somewhere in the Monster World...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ケイブリスが出撃する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Cavebris takes the field.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類軍、陣地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Human army, positions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 撤収しようとしたランスの前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As Lance was trying to retreat,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ケイブリスが現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Cavebris appears.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、ケイブリス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, Cavebris.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 部下に戦えと命じて自分は隠れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Orders his subordinates to fight while he hides.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦いが始まって５日
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Five days after the battle started.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 攻撃限界点になった人類は撤退
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The humans reach their attack limit and retreat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦いが始まって２週間
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two weeks since the battle began.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類軍は魔物界全土を制圧
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The human army has taken control of the entire Monster World.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人ケイブリスを発見、ランスが向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They found the demon Cavebris; Lance heads there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ルッコンフード洞窟内
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Inside Luconfood Cave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 入ります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Entering.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ルッコンフード洞窟
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Luconfood Cave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 恐瘴気が広がる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A terrifying miasma spreads.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、最奥の部屋
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, in the innermost room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスが乱心、ストロガノフを殺す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cavebris goes mad and kills Stroganoff.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか魔王になろうと焦っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He is desperately trying to become the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ルッコンフード洞窟、最奥の部屋
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Luconfood Cave, innermost room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスを追い詰め、戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cornering Cavebris, the battle begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ケイブリスを倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated Demon King Cavebris.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やったー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We did it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍が魔王を捜している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon army is searching for the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスは魔王を殺すつもり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cavebris intends to kill the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勇者も捜している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are also searching for the hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスもエッチの為に探索を命じた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance also ordered exploration for lewd purposes.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the end, everyone fights Miki together.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＪＡＰＡＮ城、ランス達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: JAPAN Castle, Lance and the others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 橋のおかげで守れているが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are being protected thanks to the bridge,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 橋のおかげで攻め込む事も出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But because of the bridge, they cannot attack either.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達の拠点ＪＡＰＡＮ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance's base, JAPAN.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、魔物の猛攻と妖怪の内乱でついて滅亡
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, it was destroyed due to a fierce monster assault and a yokai internal conflict.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物界、ケイブリスの本拠地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Monster World, Cavebris's stronghold.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスの美樹への暴力と陵辱が続く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cavebris continues to abuse and violate Miki.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物界、ケイブリスの本拠地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Monster World, Cavebris's stronghold.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美樹を殺してついにケイブリスが魔王になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Having killed Miki, Cavebris finally became the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、参謀本部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, General Staff Headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各地の軍の再配置を進めている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rearranging troops from various areas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ４地域から魔軍を全て追い出した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They have driven out all the demon armies from the four regions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、問題は解決した訳では無い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, the problem has not been solved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, Command Center.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスが魔物界に攻め込む作戦を発表する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance announces a plan to invade the Monster World.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, Command Center.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各地から兵力２０万を集める
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gathering 200,000 troops from various regions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦争の準備を進めています
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are preparing for war.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 番裏の砦、ヘルマン＆リーザス軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ban'ura Fort, Hermann & Liezas army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジノライン、ゼス＆自由都市＆ＪＡＰＡＮ軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maginot Line, Zess, Free City, and JAPAN armies.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの指示で突撃開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Charge begins under Lance's orders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 序盤の戦況状況
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Situation in the early stages of the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類は勢いで攻め込み、志気も高い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Human forces are attacking with momentum and high morale.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍は数は居るが志気は低い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon army has numbers but low morale.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、魔物界のどこか・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, somewhere in the Monster World...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ケイブリスが出撃する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Cavebris takes the field.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類軍、陣地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Human army, positions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 撤収しようとしたランスの前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As Lance was trying to retreat,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ケイブリスが現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Cavebris appears.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、ケイブリス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, Cavebris.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 部下に戦えと命じて自分は隠れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Orders his subordinates to fight while he hides.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦いが始まって５日
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Five days after the battle started.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 攻撃限界点になった人類は撤退
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The humans reach their attack limit and retreat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦いが始まって２週間
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two weeks since the battle began.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類軍は魔物界全土を制圧
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The human army has taken control of the entire Monster World.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人ケイブリスを発見、ランスが向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They found the demon Cavebris; Lance heads there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ルッコンフード洞窟内
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Inside Luconfood Cave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 入ります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Entering.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ルッコンフード洞窟
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Luconfood Cave.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 恐瘴気が広がる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A terrifying miasma spreads.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、最奥の部屋
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, in the innermost room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスが乱心、ストロガノフを殺す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cavebris goes mad and kills Stroganoff.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか魔王になろうと焦っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He is desperately trying to become the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ルッコンフード洞窟、最奥の部屋
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Luconfood Cave, innermost room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスを追い詰め、戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cornering Cavebris, the battle begins.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ケイブリスを倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated Demon King Cavebris.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やったー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We did it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍が魔王を捜している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon army is searching for the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスは魔王を殺すつもり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cavebris intends to kill the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勇者も捜している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are also searching for the hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスもエッチの為に探索を命じた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance also ordered exploration for lewd purposes.
